title: Killing.Floor.2.Ultimate.Launcher.V3-Royalgamer06.rar
description:
Killing Floor 2 Ultimate Launcher by Royalgamer06

Changelog V3:
- Fixed stats saving for offline play
- Added game length option for offline/online play
- Added game password and admin password in hosting options
- Added max players in hosting options
- Changed launcher name to "Ultimate Launcher" (sounds better)
- Bug fixes and improvements

Notes:
ONLINE STAT SAVING IS BEING WORKED ON!
Launcher only supports game v1002 offline. Online and offline both work in game v1001.

Instructions:
Extract the contents of this archive into your game root folder.

Game crash?
Install the redist in _Commonredist

Your server not in serverlist?
Make sure you port forward port 7777-7778 and 27005-27015. 
And check if your firewall isn't blocking anything.
Restart Steam
